RACE.FOOTNOTES: LADY DE BERRY tracked two wide, then between horses into the far turn, shifted four wide entering the lane, rallied to drive past the leaders at the furlong grounds and drew clear. JUSTDENY stalked in the three path, ranged up outside of the leading pair turning for home, bid along with an outer rival t the furlong grounds but was outkicked and proved second best. HIDDEN PRESENCE pursued two wide and between horses, shifted out in midstretch and stayed on to edge show. FLORIBUNDA tracked along the inside, shifted out and vied for show into the final furlong but was bested by an outer foe. MISS HARMONIC saved ground in midpack and ran on between horses. LAURISTON (IRE) hopped at the start and was off slow, lacked speed in the three to two path, split foes four wide at the furlong grounds and ran on willingly. DAZZLIN' DICTATOR lacked speed along the inside, took the far turn in the three path and failed to factor. BROUGHTY FERRY trailed, took the far turn in the four path, entered the lane in the six path and moved up. ADRASTEIA set the pace inside of a prompting foe, but was overhauled by bidders in midstretch and weakened. THORNY laid off of the pace in the two to three path, but was blocked at the furlong grounds and offered no bid. CLEOPATRA'S NILE pursued three wide, but floated five wide turning for home and weakened. GOLD DEL MAR prompted two wide but caved between horses entering the lane.
